---
import HeaderButton from "./HeaderButton.astro";
---

<header class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-xl lg:py-16 lg:px-6">
  <div class="mx-auto text-center mb-8 lg:mb-16">
    <h2
      class="mb-4 text-5xl font-extrabold uppercase text-transparent bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-200 via-gray-300 to-green-600 bg-clip-text"
    >
      about &lt;me/&gt;
    </h2>
  </div>
  <HeaderButton />
  <section class="col-span-full global-grid py-4 md:py-96 lg:py-7 space-y-24">
    <div
      class="text-gray-300 col-span-full lg:text-base leading-7 mt-6 space-y-7 md:text-18 md:space-y-4 lg:text-20 xl:col-span-6"
    >
      <p>
        I started out as a left brainer and enjoyed coding using <span
          class="font-extrabold">Java</span
        > and <span class="font-extrabold">MySQL</span> in the early days of
        high school. Couple years later I developed an addiction for web design
        and I&apos;m enthusiastic about making designs look and feel good
        through front-end development.
      </p>
      <p>
        I have a knack for working with <span class="font-extrabold"
          >design systems</span
        >. Be it designing them from scratch or engineering them with the power
        of SCSS and Storybook.
      </p>
      <p>
        I&apos;m a cheerful person with decent marketing skills. I fancy
        teaching and learning anything website related (you should check out my
        IG <a href="https://instagram.com/mujs.dev" target="_blank">@mujs.dev</a
        >). In my spare time, I sleep, drink water, and hunt for trophies on my
        PS5.
      </p>
      <p>A brief list of tech goodies I&apos;ve been using:</p>
      <div
        class="space-y-16 flex flex-col text-14 md:text-16 md:flex-row md:space-y-0 md:space-x-64 lg:text-18"
      >
        <div class="space-y-8 flex flex-col">
          <div>
            <span>👨‍🎨</span> Figma
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>👨‍🎨</span> Adobe Xd
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>👨‍🎨</span> Webflow
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>👨‍🎨</span> Stripo
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-8 flex flex-col">
          <div>
            <span>💻</span> HTML, SCSS, JS
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>💻</span> Vue, React, Next.js
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>💻</span> Storybook
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>💻</span> Handlebars
          </div>
          <div>
            <span>💻</span> Ruby on rails (a tad)
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</header>
